nodes.text: Dr'xureretue was an Ishi Tib who owned Docking Bay 87 in Mos Eisley. His insisted on being called "Drue" since most people could not pronounce his name properly. Drue had a cheerful personality who introduced newcomers to the laws and habits of Mos Eisley, and was a good source of information and gossip. He owned two labor droids that handled the unloading and loading of cargo. Despite his good nature, he was very punctual when it came to fees and business practices.
